{"tid":1707381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"截至今晨警方過去一星期共拘捕266人，最細為11歲","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:11:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ebf36d35cb915ff1f8e6a1e9f991cd2b55b2d0","tid":1707381,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"警察公共關係科總警司謝振中表示，截至今早凌晨，警方在過去一星期共拘捕266人，年齡介乎11至74歲，涉嫌非法集結、藏有攻擊性武器、意圖謀殺等罪。另外，有18名警員在執行職務期間受傷，其中一人仍然留醫。<br />\n謝振中表示，警方在上星期二發射過7發催淚彈、5發橡膠子彈、2發布袋彈及1發海棉彈；在上星期五就發射過136發催淚彈、27發橡膠子彈、3發布袋彈及8發海棉彈。<br />\n警方又說，昨日在又一城有示威者意圖搶犯，又襲擊在場的警員，有一名警員的眼部受傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1491372_1_20191111171554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1491372_1_20191111171554.jpg&h=ff85dbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491372-20191111.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491372-20191111.htm&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2ByIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=4082024c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491372-20191111.htm&h=971099a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491372-20191111.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dc8ff8982d2e85202df1dc84a0075d7fa85942c6","tid":1707381,"uid":105976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"仲幻想緊市民會覺得警察受傷慘慘豬 會割席<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港市民係想黑警全部殉職"},{"pid":"918d292b0e3b5f3a3eeaae7d1657cec4eb112ae4","tid":1707381,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"11-74歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br 